summary:
Danbeau headcanon time to fix the mess with the timelines that the mcu made!
SO! The accident that gave Monica her powers...
body:
Danbeau headcanon time to fix the mess with the timelines that the mcu made!

SO! The accident that gave Monica her powers happened when she was around 19 while she was in college, becoming spectrum and later an agent of shield working for Fury and Carols partner.

Since Monica and Carol age so much slower, Maria decided that she didn’t want to leave her family alone so soon, so the three of them had some serious time conversation about what to do… Carol asked Nick for help, and some scientist from shield experimented with Kree blood and gave Maria a serum that would make her age at the same rate that her family.

THE END! problem fixed. Danbeau family forever… now Maria “photon” Rambeau pilots them on missions in space while the three of them kick Kree a*s and defend earth.

Ko-fi

summary: are you still doing these? if so: sleeping with carol danvers? otherwise just ignore this lmao love your blog btw💕
question: are you still doing these? if so: sleeping with carol danvers? otherwise just ignore this lmao love your blog btw💕
answer:
I’m happy you like my blog pal

“Fuck…” 

You awake to the sound of her voice mixed with the shaking of the vanity. You stifle a yawn as you sit up in bed, spying Carol trying to quietly pick up the items that were now scattered on the floor.

“Carol?” You mumble quietly, rubbing your eyes slowly. “What are you doing?”

“I didn’t mean to wake you.” The blonde apologizes, a soft chuckle leaving her lips.  

“You coming to bed?”

“Mhmm,” she assures you, “I’ll be there in a minute.”

“Okay,” You lay back down, shuffling to get comfortable. “don’t take too long.”

“I won’t,” Carol disappears into the bathroom leaving you alone. You try to wait up for her but drowsiness takes over and you’re back to sleep before you know it.

summary:
Ngl I hated Captain Marvel for two reasons;
1) The Skrulls are evil bastards who love nothing more than to wage war on everyone....
body:
Ngl I hated Captain Marvel for two reasons;

1) The Skrulls are evil bastards who love nothing more than to wage war on everyone. They waged war on Xandar. They waged war on the Badoon they waged war on Karolina Dean’s race (I forget their name). They conquer, colonise and subjugate. They are just as bad as, if not worse than, the Kree. The suns never set on the Skrull Empire (or the Kree or even the Spartoi, but we’re not talking about them). They’re bloodthirsty, battle crazy and when they’re around you can’t even trust your pet goldfish.

But Marvel went and made them ‘victims’. Like no. Fuck that shit. I hate it. I want Secret Empire. I want a Fantastic Four movie. I want a second Fantastic Four movie where the Skrulls attack and Reed Richards hypnotises them into cows. Give me my evil Skrulls, you cowards!

2) The cat. Her name is Chewie. HER NAME IS CHEWIE.
